Class LogInsightClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.loginsightapi.LogInsightClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class LogInsightClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    LogInsight client class providing mechanisms to connect to LogInsight, Query loginsight and ingest messages to loginsight

      • connect

        public void connect(java.lang.String userName,
                    java.lang.String password)
             throws AuthFailure
        Connects to LogInsight and initialize AsyncHttpClient with LogInsight session Id. This method should be called after a successful authentication with LogInsight, so that getSessionId returns a proper session id.
        Parameters:
        userName - name of the user
        password - password of the user
        Throws:
        AuthFailure - authentication failure exception

      • messageQuery

        public MessageQueryResponse messageQuery(java.lang.String apiUrl)
                                  throws LogInsightApiException
        This method uses CloseableHttpAsyncClient to execute the remote query. Callers should ensure that connect() is invoked before calling this method.
        Parameters:
        apiUrl - for LogInsight 3.0 API. The URL looks like text/CONTAINS+Test/timestamp/GT+0
        Returns:
        a JSONObject representing the LI response
        Throws:
        LogInsightApiException - general LogInsightApiException
